Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.29,note,,0,0,0,,{\a5}註：捏他自《鐵人28號》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,飛拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,飛踢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了 不見了不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了不見了不見了不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不見了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西不見了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(84,45)}{\c&HAE412B&\bord4\3c&HE4E77D&\fs18\shad3\4c&H9F3C28&\move(360,118,345,118)}翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.77,0:00:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(84,45)}{\c&H7F612D&\3c&HF2D59D&\bord3\fs15\move(395,140,380,140)}科學家{\blur3\fs19\c&HEFEBD3&}驚{\blur0\c&H7F612D&\3c&HF2D59D&\bord3\fs15}惶{\blur3\fs19\c&HEFEBD3&}失{\blur0\c&H7F612D&\3c&HF2D59D&\bord3\fs15}措
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是遙控器啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,心情可好啊 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了 叫四神來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,又在找東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,開始搜索～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,有勞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把作業系統裝進去也就一樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.02,0:01:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以都跟你說要裝個GPS了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.91,0:01:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,才不需要呢 又不可能會丟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.51,0:01:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再說 昨天白天的時候還在的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天白天…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.77,0:01:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別邊吃邊說話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.65,0:01:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,別撐著桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再來點醬汁～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,自己去倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有客人?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,把那三傻瓜交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是遊戲控
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是宅女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我的遙控器在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,別裝不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,淨說些聽不懂的胡話 腦子被敲了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.36,0:02:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你個死假小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就給我到家外面去玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,目前 鞍馬寺正進行臨時安全檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:57.81,note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}今天怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,請諸位配合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,重複一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.38,0:03:07.13,note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}目前 鞍馬寺正進行臨時安全檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.13,0:03:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,鄉下地方一直都亂糟糟鬧哄哄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不過今天似乎格外熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,八瀨童子!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多人一大早就在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,鞍馬寺的人還真閒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看您說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我們尊貴的八瀨童子 是不是又在準備茶會呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,做一個內心和錢包都很充裕的家裡蹲真好呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,站住 你這隻鳥!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,告辭了 八瀨童子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下個路口左側 馬上無路可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我的遙控器到底跑哪去啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 是三月食堂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有哪有 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我有點事想詢問一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 諸位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,多謝啦 辛苦啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是伏見 幹得漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.45,0:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我很瞭解你的 你可能幹了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有哪有哪有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 你怎麼找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要保密哦 不然她會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,放開喝 喝個痛快!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:56.01,note,,0,0,0,,{\a6}遙控器 遙控器 遙控器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,幸虧裝了GPS 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
